=== 0004_CTO037415_в•©вҢЎв•ҷвҲ©в–’ПҶ.dita ===
Glossary       Term Explanation    PFI      Platform of microorganisms Fast Identification software (PFI) is an automated analysis system developed based on the Linux operating system. It includes multiple analysis modules such as data filtering, microbial identification, antibiotic resistance gene annotation, virulence factor annotation, and de novo assembly.      MPS      Massively Parallel Sequencing (MPS), generally refers